  "description": "A compact refrigerator with a transparent tempered glass door, presented on the market by the popular brand Whirlpool in 2024. This model is primarily designed to accommodate drinks and food products in an office, store or administrative building. The cooling chamber is equipped with three shelves, which can be adjusted in height if necessary. The useful capacity is 127 liters. Inside, you can place up to 62 bottles (cans) with a volume of 0.5 liters. The Whirlpool ADN 140 B refrigerated cabinet allows you to set the temperature in the range from +7 to +14 °C. The device is equipped with an automatic defrosting system. The compressor has a reliable rotary design, the operating noise of the refrigeration system reaches 38 dB. The door leaf supports reversible hinges. The transparent tempered glass door has an aluminum frame. The average annual energy consumption is 238 kWh.",
